  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2009-04-29",
    "date": "2009-06-01T19:01:44Z",
    "text": "Amateur Radio Emergency Communications Enhancement Act of 2009 - Directs the Secretary of Homeland Security to: (1) study the uses and capabilities of amateur radio communications in emergencies and disaster relief; (2) use the expertise of the American Radio Relay League in the study; and (3) report to Congress."
